issue.title: [CF 316] Rune of Zeth Trink
issue.body:
Submitted Via

Curse Client 4.0.1.112, Microsoft Windows NT 6.0.6002 Service Pack 2

Installed Version

4.6.3

Description

It cannot track the FL Rune of Zeth trinket. It can track the buff; however, it cannot track the CD. I tried to type the name, shift click, and drag the icon from my spell bar into the grid. Nothing gets it to recognize the trink.

Installed Addons

AuctionLite - v1.8.2 Calculator - Calculator 1.6 GatherMate2 - 1.15.2 GatherMate2_Data - v6.8 HealBot Continued - 4.2.2.2 MoveAnything - 12.2.0 OmniCC - 4.2.3 Postal - v3.4.10 Quartz - 3.0.7 Recount - v4.2.0f release Routes - v1.4.1 TellMeWhen - 4.6.3


> Posted by CurseForge user PurpleMurp | Imported from CurseForge issue #316 | Raw
